Class CoreServicesCallbackHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.ufc.storm.wservices.CoreServicesCallbackHandler

  • public abstract class CoreServicesCallbackHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    CoreServicesCallbackHandler Callback class, Users can extend this class and implement their own receiveResult and receiveError methods.

    • Constructor Summary

      CoreServicesCallbackHandler()
      Please use this constructor if you don't want to set any clientData
      CoreServicesCallbackHandler(java.lang.Object clientData)
      User can pass in any object that needs to be accessed once the NonBlocking Web service call is finished and appropriate method of this CallBack is called.
